sankham ( english : conch ) is a 2009 telugu action film , produced by j bhagavan , j pulla rao on sri balaji cine media banner and directed by siva .   starring gopichand , trisha krishnan in lead roles and music composed by s. thaman .   the film recorded as flop at box office .   the film was dubbed in hindi as phir ek most wanted and in tamil as sivappu saamy .